data.description: This expansive 5-bedroom residence boasts Double Master bedrooms. The main floor primary bedroom includes a private bathroom and walk-in closet. The second-floor primary bedroom features a walk-in closet, private bathroom, and access to a private balcony. The second floor also offers a generous loft area suitable for an additional living space, laundry room and 3 additional bedrooms. Outside, a covered patio and a fenced yard with a utility shed for extra storage enhance the property. With its great features and price, this home is a fantastic opportunity. Schedule your showing today to explore all it has to offer!
